{"tid":1049958,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"禍不單行 雲尼斯奧斯唞兩個月","createTime":"2019-03-06T16:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T17:43:39.000Z","uid":186071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"273b74e0bf3fa3c2a86321e56159105c8534cd5b","tid":1049958,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhajPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=7750aeb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里於周三證實，巴西前鋒雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞於歐聯對阿積士時受傷，經診斷後確認右足踝韌帶撕裂，預計唞兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞（Vinicius Junior）是於周二歐聯16強次回合鬥阿積士時上半場傷出，當時他在場上不禁落淚，而球隊在這場比賽最終以1:4敗陣，兩回合計以3:5被踢出局，衛冕失敗。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬於周三發表聲明公佈這個壞消息：「雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞的右足踝確診韌帶撕裂。」官方並沒評估其傷勢，但西班牙傳媒估計他需要休息兩個月，由於皇馬已於兩個盃賽出局，意味即使雲尼斯奧斯在5月復出，屆時能夠參加的比賽亦不會多。<br />\n<br />\n除了皇馬受影響，連帶他在國家隊的發展也受影響，最近首獲召用的他，將錯過本月稍後對巴拿馬及捷克的兩場比賽。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956a7d4247ca4bb7308db39f6999e2f9b07e8e42","tid":1049958,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"個黑鬼係幾扭得 但唔勁囉 憑咩場場正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ccd3595963f7cdf6b924babddd76fc796a4f05","tid":1049958,"uid":18395,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"956a7d4247ca4bb7308db39f6999e2f9b07e8e42","tid":1049958,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"個黑鬼係幾扭得 但唔勁囉 憑咩場場正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"因為其他更廢<img src=\"/assets